The paper focuses on improving the design of Capsule Networks for image classification, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the comparison of Capsule Networks with other deep learning models, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NE). Additionally, the dataset used in the experiments involves American Sign Language, which could be categorized under natural language processing (cs.CL).
